text: The Witch (stylized as The VVitch, and subtitled A New-England Folktale) is a 2015 folk horror movie written and directed by Robert Eggers. It stars Anya Taylor-Joy, Ralph Ineson, Kate Dickie, Harvey Scrimshaw, Ellie Grainger, and Lucas Dawson. It is set in 1630s New England and is about a Puritan family who find forces of evil in the woods near their farm. ==References== Category:2015 horror movies Category:Movies directed by Robert Eggers Category:American horror movies Category:Canadian horror movies Category:Universal Pictures movies
